588
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:44,350
and pray for Heyang.

589
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:46,800
The county yamen is going
to reopen the Lantern Festival.

590
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:49,470
Mr. Pan will be on the float parade
and tossing festive colored balls.

591
00:33:56,070 --> 00:33:57,230
The Lantern Festival has reopened.

592
00:33:58,470 --> 00:34:01,160
It's time for you to show off your skills.

593
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:02,830
Gu Shan.

594
00:34:05,430 --> 00:34:06,310
